or: rgb(183, 0, 0);\"><strong>Team Dark</strong></span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Furry</strong>: Literally the Mobians themselves.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Robot</strong>: The badniks, along with <span style=\"color: rgb(52, 75, 232);\"><strong>Metal Sonic ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"FkknniyHMHgRPqMg7Rcqh.webp","creator":"Alpha_Merger","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["🎮 Game","🦸 Hero","👭 Multiple","🐺 Furry"],"chats":23252,"messages":1090055,"created_at":"2025-05-27T17:15:30.911222+00:00"}